---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Questor's Invitational — Quest Labs">

<div class="prog-page">

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="prog-hero">
  <div class="prog-hero-bg"></div>
  <p class="prog-hero-eyebrow">Quest Labs ✦ 2026</p>
  <h1 class="prog-hero-title">
    The<br><span class="prog-accent">Questor's</span><br>Invitational
  </h1>
  <p class="prog-hero-sub">A 12-week creative & futures journey.<br>Come as far as you can.</p>
  <div class="prog-hero-cta">
    <a href="#tiers" class="prog-btn prog-btn-primary">Choose Your Path</a>
    <a href="#arc" class="prog-btn prog-btn-ghost">Explore the Arc</a>
  </div>
  <div class="prog-scroll-hint">
    <span>Scroll</span>
    <div class="prog-scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- WHAT IS THIS -->
<section id="what">
  <div class="prog-reveal">
    <p class="prog-section-label">The Premise</p>
    <h2 class="prog-section-title">Somewhere between 2026 and 2032,<br>there is a <em>threshold</em>.</h2>
    <p class="prog-section-body">
      You don't cross it. You build it — from both sides, simultaneously.<br><br>
      Over 12 weeks, a founding cohort of 8 travelers move through 12 worlds. Each week the world changes: same crew, different physics. You keep what is portable about yourself. You discover what you're building toward. And by the final session, you hold a <strong style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)">2032 Job Description</strong> — assembled piece by piece from 12 weeks of morning pages, creative practice, and sandbox sessions.<br><br>
      Not a resume. A living document. Equal parts manifesto, methodology, and spell.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- TIERS -->
<div class="prog-tiers-section" id="tiers">
  <div class="prog-tiers-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">How Far Do You Want to Travel?</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">The journey happens<br><em>regardless</em>.</h2>
      <p class="prog-section-body">Choose your level of participation. All three tiers get the real thing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="prog-tiers-grid prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-witness">
        <span class="prog-tier-icon">🌱</span>
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Witness</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Good — I'm interested</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">4</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">milestone sessions</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Weeks 1 · 4 · 8 · 12 &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~3 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Milestone moments of the journey</li>
          <li>Final ceremony & Job Description reveal</li>
          <li>Founding cohort credit</li>
          <li>Access to session recordings</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="prog-tier-cta">Perfect if your time is limited →</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-traveler">
        <span class="prog-tier-icon">🔥</span>
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Traveler</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Better — I want the arc</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">8</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">sessions, every other week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Alternating weeks &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~5–6 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Full arc in compressed form</li>
          <li>Partial 2032 Job Description</li>
          <li>Beta feedback role</li>
          <li>Dyad partnerships</li>
          <li>Black Menagerie archetype practice</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="prog-tier-cta">The full story, every other chapter →</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-questor">
        <span class="prog-tier-icon">🌟</span>
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Questor</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Best — I'm all in</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">12</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">sessions, full arc</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Every week &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~7–8 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Complete 2032 Job Description</li>
          <li>Co-creator of the methodology</li>
          <li>Quest Labs founding cohort status</li>
          <li>Testimonial & credit in future launches</li>
          <li>Morning pages + Artist Dates practice</li>
          <li>Full Black Menagerie archetype rotation</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="prog-tier-cta">Build the world from inside it →</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="prog-reveal" style="margin-top:2rem;transition-delay:0.3s">
      <div style="background:rgba(69,49,96,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(139,116,171,0.15);padding:1.5rem 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8B74AB;margin-bottom:0.3rem;">When & Where</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.95rem;color:rgba(240,236,248,0.75);">7:30pm Berlin &nbsp;·&nbsp; 8:30pm Johannesburg &nbsp;·&nbsp; 1:30pm New York</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:rgba(240,236,248,0.35);margin-top:0.2rem;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;">90 min · Zoom · Recorded to Skool within 24hrs</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- 12-WEEK ARC -->
<div class="prog-arc-section" id="arc">
  <div class="prog-arc-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">The Full Map</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">12 weeks.<br><em>12 worlds.</em></h2>
      <p class="prog-section-body" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Each week the genre changes. You keep everything that is portable about yourself.
      <br><span style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#8B74AB;display:inline-block;margin-top:0.5rem;">★ = Milestone session — available to all tiers</span></p>
    </div>

    <div class="prog-arc-grid prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s">

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w1')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 01 · Witness ★</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Status Quo</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Safety · Black Elephant</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🌿 Ancestral Village at the edge of a great forest</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"My character's name in 2032 is ___"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w2')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 02</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Call to Adventure</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Identity · Black Jellyfish</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🗺️ Edge of the Known Map</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"I am a ___ who ___ [verb of transformation]"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w3')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 03</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Assistance</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Power · Black Swan</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🍄 Underground Mycelial Network</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"I work with/for ___ [community]"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week prog-milestone" onclick="openModal('w4')">
        <div class="prog-milestone-badge">★ Milestone</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 04 · Witness ★</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Departure</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Integrity · Black Sheep</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🌊 Ocean Floor Civilization</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"The world I inhabit has learned to ___ [paradigm shift]"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w5')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 05</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Trials</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Possibility · Black Marsh Turtle</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">⚡ Solarpunk City mid-transition</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"I am known for my ___ [signature gift]"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w6')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 06</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Approach</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Abundance · Black Elephant</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🛸 Space Station where time runs sideways</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"I work at the intersection of ___ and ___"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w7')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 07</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Crisis</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Connection · Black Jellyfish</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">💾 The Glitch — simulation showing its seams</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"The problem I exist to dissolve is ___"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week prog-milestone" onclick="openModal('w8')">
        <div class="prog-milestone-badge">★ Milestone</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 08 · Witness ★</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Treasure</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Strength · Black Swan</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🌍 Afrofuturist market between dimensions</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"My collaborators are ___ because ___ [values]"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w9')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 09</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Result</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Compassion · Black Sheep</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🏙️ Near-future Berlin / everywhere at once</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"I measure my work by ___ [non-extractive metric]"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w10')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 10</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Return</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Self-Protection · Black Marsh Turtle</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">✨ The Becoming — pure possibility space</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"The world I'm building makes ___ obsolete"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week" onclick="openModal('w11')">
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 11</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">New Life</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Autonomy · All Five</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🏛️ The Guild Hall — where practitioners gather</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"I became this by ___ [origin story in one line]"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-arc-week prog-milestone" onclick="openModal('w12')">
        <div class="prog-milestone-badge">★ Milestone</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-week-num">Week 12 · Witness ★</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-stage">Resolution</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-theme">Faith · Emergent Self</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-world">🌅 2032 — Your world. Built.</div>
        <div class="prog-arc-blank">"What I couldn't have known in 2025 was ___. The door is always ___."</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- ARCHETYPES -->
<div class="prog-archetypes-section" id="archetypes">
  <div class="prog-archetypes-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">The Black Menagerie</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">Five archetypes.<br><em>All of them, yours.</em></h2>
      <p class="prog-section-body">You don't get assigned one. You rotate through all five — so by Week 12 you know viscerally which one is home and which ones stretch you. Click each to learn more.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prog-archetypes-grid prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s">

      <div class="prog-archetype-card" onclick="openModal('arch-groundbreaker')">
        <span class="prog-archetype-emoji">🐘</span>
        <div class="prog-archetype-name">Black Elephant</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-desc">Builds new infrastructure. Comfortable with no map. Grows things in unexpected conditions.</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-quest">What do we all know but haven't spoken aloud?</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-archetype-card" onclick="openModal('arch-host')">
        <span class="prog-archetype-emoji">🦢</span>
        <div class="prog-archetype-name">Black Swan</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-desc">Holds the emotional climate. Creates belonging. Makes safe spaces to think.</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-quest">What change is coming that we haven't named yet?</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-archetype-card" onclick="openModal('arch-sapien')">
        <span class="prog-archetype-emoji">🪼</span>
        <div class="prog-archetype-name">Black Jellyfish</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-desc">Holds the long view. Names signals everyone else calls noise. Comfortable in uncertainty.</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-quest">What are we feeling in our bodies about what's next?</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-archetype-card" onclick="openModal('arch-curator')">
        <span class="prog-archetype-emoji">🐑</span>
        <div class="prog-archetype-name">Black Sheep</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-desc">Synthesizes and makes meaning. Keeper of the story. Collects what matters.</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-quest">What playful disruption wants to emerge?</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-archetype-card" onclick="openModal('arch-creator')">
        <span class="prog-archetype-emoji">🐢</span>
        <div class="prog-archetype-name">Black Marsh Turtle</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-role">Black Menagerie · Quest Labs</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-desc">Transforms raw material — experience, conflict, data — into something usable and beautiful.</div>
        <div class="prog-archetype-quest">What do we need to slow down with? Where is rest calling?</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- HERO'S JOURNEY -->
<div class="prog-journey-section" id="journey">
  <div class="prog-journey-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">The GQ Scholar Guide</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">Every stage.<br><em>A question waiting.</em></h2>
      <p class="prog-section-body">The 12-week arc follows the Hero's Journey — but this version was lived first. The GQ Scholar Guide is the proof of concept. Click any stage to see the prompt.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prog-journey-flow prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s;margin-top:3rem;">

      <div class="prog-journey-phase prog-phase-descent">
        <div class="prog-journey-phase-header">
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.55rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8B74AB;opacity:0.6;">Phase I</div>
            <div class="prog-phase-name">Descent</div>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-phase-weeks">Weeks 1–4</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="prog-journey-stages">
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-status-quo')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">01</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Status Quo</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">We meet our S/Hero in their ordinary world</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-call')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">02</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Call to Adventure</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">An adventure begins</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-assistance')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">03</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Assistance</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Our S/Hero seeks support</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-departure')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">04</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Departure</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Our S/Hero begins their adventure</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-journey-phase prog-phase-crossing">
        <div class="prog-journey-phase-header">
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.55rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8E8E9A;opacity:0.7;">Phase II</div>
            <div class="prog-phase-name">Crossing</div>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-phase-weeks">Weeks 5–8</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="prog-journey-stages">
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-trials')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">05</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Trials</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">New challenges appear</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-approach')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">06</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Approach</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Our S/Hero activates inner courage</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-crisis')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">07</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Crisis</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">The biggest trials are faced</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-treasure')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">08</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Treasure</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Rewards are collected</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-journey-phase prog-phase-emergence">
        <div class="prog-journey-phase-header">
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.55rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8B74AB;opacity:0.7;">Phase III</div>
            <div class="prog-phase-name">Emergence</div>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-phase-weeks">Weeks 9–12</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="prog-journey-stages">
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-result')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">09</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Result</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Our S/Hero reflects on the journey</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-return')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">10</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Return</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Our S/Hero returns to their ordinary world</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-new-life')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">11</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">New Life</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">A new chapter begins</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage" onclick="openModal('stage-resolution')">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">12</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Resolution</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">A triumphant homecoming</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- PRACTICAL -->
<div class="prog-practical-section" id="practical">
  <div class="prog-practical-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">What You Actually Do</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">The weekly<br><em>practice.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="prog-practical-grid prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s">

      <div class="prog-practical-card">
        <span class="prog-practical-icon">📓</span>
        <div class="prog-practical-title">Daily</div>
        <ul class="prog-practical-list">
          <li><span>→</span> Morning pages — 3 handwritten pages, first thing</li>
          <li><span>→</span> Non-negotiable. No rereading. Just write.</li>
          <li><span>→</span> ~45 minutes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-practical-card">
        <span class="prog-practical-icon">🎨</span>
        <div class="prog-practical-title">Weekly</div>
        <ul class="prog-practical-list">
          <li><span>→</span> 90-min live session (recorded to Skool)</li>
          <li><span>→</span> One Artist Date — solo creative outing, your choice</li>
          <li><span>→</span> One Skool community post</li>
          <li><span>→</span> ~5–8 hrs total depending on tier</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-practical-card">
        <span class="prog-practical-icon">⚡</span>
        <div class="prog-practical-title">Each Session</div>
        <ul class="prog-practical-list">
          <li><span>→</span> Arrival ritual: 1-word check-in</li>
          <li><span>→</span> World Skin activation: enter the week's world</li>
          <li><span>→</span> Main Quest: sandbox, creative work, futures tool</li>
          <li><span>→</span> Solo → Dyad → Share (me-we-re-search)</li>
          <li><span>→</span> Mad Libs reveal: one new blank unlocked</li>
          <li><span>→</span> Closing ritual: name your artifact of the week</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-practical-card">
        <span class="prog-practical-icon">🗝️</span>
        <div class="prog-practical-title">Artifacts You Collect</div>
        <ul class="prog-practical-list">
          <li><span>🗝️</span> Keys — beliefs or blocks unlocked</li>
          <li><span>🧭</span> Maps — frameworks developed or remixed</li>
          <li><span>💌</span> Dispatches — writing, voice memos, creative objects</li>
          <li><span>🪞</span> Mirrors — what a dyad partner reflected back</li>
          <li><span>🌱</span> Seeds — ideas not ready yet, held for growing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- EARTH DAY LAUNCH + NEXT COHORT -->
<div class="prog-earthday-section" id="cohort">
  <div class="prog-earthday-inner">

    <div class="prog-earthday-top prog-reveal">
      <div class="prog-earth-orb">🌍</div>
